{"tid":2094283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【突發】康文署：公共圖書館覆檢部分書籍會否違反港區國安法","createTime":"2020-07-04T13:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T17:16:24.000Z","uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"fa1deff549d5ee979e613dc41b07718345f7985f","tid":2094283,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T13:33:03.000Z","msg":"前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒、公民黨立法會議員陳淑莊及《香港城邦論》作者陳雲的數部著作，暫時無法在公共圖書館借閱，網頁顯示，有關書籍「覆檢中」。康文署回覆查詢時表示，公共圖書館將覆檢部份書籍的內容會否違反《港區國安法》，有關書籍將暫時不會給予市民借閱和作參考用途。<br />\n<br />\n康文署表示，公共圖書館的館藏必須符合本港法律規定，隨著《港區國安法》立法，館方須確保圖書館藏遵守有關法例規定。<br />\n<br />\n另外，康文署指，公共圖書館的館藏發展工作是以《聯合國教育、科學及文化組織公共圖書館宣言》所訂原則為指引。"},{"pid":"24596ccce4d923a29b17c24bf17dc9a056e2f43f","tid":2094283,"uid":4239,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T13:35:56.000Z","msg":"文革2.0"},{"pid":"a7de4eb460798638392c037ce9572b23fa071029","tid":2094283,"uid":335434,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T13:37:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3.six-degrees.io/upload/media/20191208/480/c0eb7784a6e3863a80c4ca4accb94716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.six-degrees.io%2Fupload%2Fmedia%2F20191208%2F480%2Fc0eb7784a6e3863a80c4ca4accb94716.jpg&h=b7cfefde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「焚書新時代」正式啟動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3283aa3b213c496c6497a5903d1c24679e999c8e","tid":2094283,"uid":288304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T13:38:21.000Z","msg":"借過書的人睇路呀<br />\n<br />\n思想撿查不遠矣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97a53ee9d9c823f